{"tid":850342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰獨立運動領袖　普伊格德蒙特：支持香港民族黨續爭自由民主","createTime":"2018-10-06T11:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T12:20:18.000Z","uid":47714,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2420cb6726b7e0ce0952ab6501ec97635c99188","tid":850342,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/加泰獨立運動領袖-普伊格德蒙特-支持香港民族黨續爭自由民主/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%B0%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96-%E6%99%AE%E4%BC%8A%E6%A0%BC%E5%BE%B7%E8%92%99%E7%89%B9-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E9%BB%A8%E7%BA%8C%E7%88%AD%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%2F&d=o4wvVtgZmRjIJ0dfGq4Tao9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0aa021ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%B0%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96-%E6%99%AE%E4%BC%8A%E6%A0%BC%E5%BE%B7%E8%92%99%E7%89%B9-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E9%BB%A8%E7%BA%8C%E7%88%AD%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%2F&h=53e980a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/加泰獨立運動領袖-普伊格德蒙特-支持香港民族黨續爭自由民主/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/spain-hk_F6puL_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fspain-hk_F6puL_1200x0.png&h=738c3451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西班牙加泰羅尼亞自治政府前主席、加泰獨立運動的主要領袖普伊格德蒙特（Carles Puigdemont），日前（10月3日）在 twitter 分享一則香港《南華早報》的報道，顯示有支持香港民族黨的市民，在10月1日當天遊行高舉「香港獨立」橫幅外，還揮舞加泰羅尼亞獨立旗幟，並叫喊「香港不是中國（Hong Kong is not China）」口號。<br />\n<br />\n普伊格德蒙特指，香港示威者揮舞著代表支持加泰獨立的旗幟 'Estelada' ，作為自由的象徵。他希望支持黃之鋒和最近被取締的香港民族黨的所有成員，繼續爭取自由和民主。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/KRLS/status/1047413324709875712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKRLS%2Fstatus%2F1047413324709875712&d=o4wvVtgZmRjIJ0dfGq4Tao9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c2c58aed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKRLS%2Fstatus%2F1047413324709875712&h=eb81f808\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/KRLS/status/1047413324709875712</a>"},{"pid":"98ae54342b95d487cd6db8f4b945489826e43915","tid":850342,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T12:09:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"467ffe24e88dd8f6b0c7332200979136d2e4a839","tid":850342,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"美國總領事館：香港政府決定令人不安，似乎與基本法原則不符<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bEDMES\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bEDMES</a><br />\n<br />\n港獨之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5836fa899d4fa322cc09743bebb9a6e3a0c3d58f","tid":850342,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T12:20:18.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒都算港獨？"}]}